# CI/CD

This section is included when `include_ci` is enabled.

The template adds GitHub Actions workflows for PDF builds and release assets.
Check repository variables and secrets before the first run.

[[% if code_listing_mode == 'external' and fetch_project_code_in_ci %]]
The workflow expects the `DIPLOMA_CODE_REPOSITORY` repository variable and the
`VIEW_DIPLOMA_CODE` secret to checkout a separate source-code repository.
[[% else %]]
A separate source-code remote repository is not required for this configuration.
[[% endif %]]
